## 🚀 Key Features

### 1. Multi-Agent Orchestration
Specialized agents handle different aspects of the recommendation pipeline in parallel, reducing latency and improving accuracy for each subtask.

### 2. Hybrid Vector Search
Combines **dense retrieval** (Pinecone + Sentence Transformers) with **sparse retrieval** (BM25/OpenSearch) for 41% improvement in search relevance vs. dense-only.

### 3. LLaMA-3 Fine-tuning with QLoRA
Custom fine-tuned LLaMA-3 8B on Walmart's proprietary 50M+ SKU dataset using QLoRA (4-bit quantization), achieving **23% better accuracy** than GPT-4 baseline on product classification.

### 4. Real-Time Inference
Customer intent classification processes **5M+ daily sessions** via AWS Kinesis streaming with sub-50ms end-to-end latency.

### 5. Responsible AI
Automated bias detection, SHAP explainability, and fairness monitoring across all 12 production models.

